  m_Name: ItJustWorks
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  id: mint_it_just_works
  displayName: It Just Works
  rulesText: mint's random values always resolve at maximum. in exchange, mint cannot crit and ignores damage multipliers -- her numbers are always the ceiling, never above it.
  flavorText: comfort incarnate. no surprises, no drama.
  designNotes: force-max on every RNG roll routed through the combat RNG chokepoint; disable crit and damage-mult application for Mint; requires combat engine to centralize randomness + multipliers.
